<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ewe, Baba Wa Mbinguni TZR107</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ewe, Baba wa Mbinguni,
 Usikie twombalo
 Hapa chini duniani,
 Na uwe radhi nalo

[V2]
 Ee Mungu, bariki
 Ndugu hawa wawili!
 Ee Mungu, bariki
 Ndugu hawa wawili!

[V3]
 Watu hawa mbele zako,
 Na mbele ya kanisa;
 Watimize Neno lako
 Wanakutana sasa.

[V4]
 Kama Yesu na Kanisa,
 Ni mmoja, na hivyo,
 Watu hawawape sasa
 Wawe mmoja vivyo

[V5]
 Walinde, Bwana, daima,
 Wabariki nyumbani
 Uwape nyingi salama
 Humu ulimwenguni.

[V6]
 Wabariki, ewe Bwana,
 Watu hawa wawili,
 Wape upaji wa wana,
 Wafurahishwe kweli.

[V7]
 Siku za duniani
 Zitakapopungua,
 Wape kurithi Mbinguni
 Mema ya kwendelea.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>107</hymn_number>
</song>